query:
SELECT a.id, a.title, d.content
            FROM (
                SELECT d.article_id, d.content
                FROM tb_article_detail AS d
                    LEFT JOIN tb_metadata AS m ON d.article_id = m.article_id
                WHERE m.id IS NULL
                LIMIT 20
            ) AS d
                JOIN tb_article AS a ON a.id = d.article_id
